in terms of getting an airplane to market, its challenges in sourcing engin=
es, and this week=E2=80=99s announcements at the Paris Air Show ( https://b=
oomsupersonic.com/flyby/boom-announces-significant-overture-program-advance=
s-at-paris-air-show ).

